content.rendered: Tingkatkan sistem keamanan bangunan dengan memasang Honeywell CADVR-2016FD. Kamera CCTV Honeywell CADVR-2016FD sangat efektif dalam menaga keamanan rumah / kantor / gedung / dlsb. DVR Honeywell CADVR-2016FD adalah produkt terbaik karena sudah dibekali:HDMI and VGA output simultaneously at up to1080P resolution H.264 High profile decoding 2 SATA HDD interface: maximum 6TB storage capacity ONVIF 2.0 compliant Support remote control through DDNS service by free of charge On-line user view: maximum 6 users simultaneously CALNVRView: free Android and Apple app for remote playback, record and snapshot through mobile phone Support 16-channel synchronized compression
